  "description": "Would be valuable to both supervisors and independent researchers",
  "body_html": "<p>One of my running theses on this blog is that <a href=\"https://substack.com/home/post/p-168415873\">there are highly skilled people that are capable of independent science</a>. But, the biggest problem is that they don't know where to find problems, don't know where the frontier is, or how to find supervisors to guide them. I myself found problems by cold emailing and networking with hundreds of people, but this is <strong>inefficient</strong>. </p><p>One the other hand, academic institutions have no money but lots of ideas they want to try. </p><p>So, we need\u2026</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!niHp!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4db9745e-b208-4c9c-9c7c-bf6101949b5f_702x366.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!niHp!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4db9745e-b208-4c9c-9c7c-bf6101949b5f_702x366.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!niHp!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4db9745e-b208-4c9c-9c7c-bf6101949b5f_702x366.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!niHp!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4db9745e-b208-4c9c-9c7c-bf6101949b5f_702x366.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!niHp!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4db9745e-b208-4c9c-9c7c-bf6101949b5f_702x366.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image